'''天主教聖保祿及明尼波利斯總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidiocesis Paulopolitana et Minneapolitana}}；{{lang-en|Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Saint Paul and Minneapolis}}）是[[美國|美國]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省[[總教區|總教區]]，也是該國三十二個總教區之一。總教區管轄[[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]]東南部十一個縣，並轄九個教區。

總教區有82萬5000名教友、187個堂區和超過400名司鐸。<ref name="History">{{cite web |title=Our History |url=https://www.archspm.org/our-history/ |publisher=Archdiocese of Saint Paul & Minneapolis |accessdate=2020-02-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212191751/https://www.archspm.org/our-history/ |archivedate=2020-02-12 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>現任總主教為{{link-en|伯爾納鐸·赫布達|Bernard Hebda|伯爾納鐸·A·赫布達}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Archbishop Bernard Hebda |url=https://www.archspm.org/leadership/archbishop-bernard-hebda/ |publisher=Archdiocese of Saint Paul & Minneapolis |accessdate=2020-02-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212182241/https://www.archspm.org/leadership/archbishop-bernard-hebda/ |archivedate=2020-02-12 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-en|安德肋·H·卡澤恩斯|Andrew H. Cozzens}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Bishop Andrew Cozzens |url=https://www.archspm.org/leadership/bishop-cozzens/ |publisher=Archdiocese of Saint Paul & Minneapolis |accessdate=2020-02-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212184528/https://www.archspm.org/leadership/bishop-cozzens/ |archivedate=2020-02-12 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-en|若望·克萊特恩·尼恩斯特德|John Clayton Nienstedt}}<ref name="Vatican20150615">{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 15.06.2015 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/06/15/0469/01027.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-02-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212190401/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/06/15/0469/01027.html |archivedate=2020-02-12 |language=it |date=2015-06-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休輔理主教為{{link-en|李·A·皮徹|Lee A. Piché|李·安多尼·皮徹}}<ref name="Vatican20150615" />。總教區於2015年時被指未能保護未成年人而任由他們受到一名[[戀童|戀童]]的[[司鐸|司鐸]]殘害，若望·尼恩斯特德和李·安多尼·皮徹於同年6月15日雙雙宣布辭去他們的總教區職務，獲[[教宗方濟各|教宗方濟各]]接納。<ref>{{cite news |title=Archbishop of St. Paul resigns over church sex scandal |url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/resignation-st-paul-minnesota-archbishop-john-nienstedt-sex-abuse-church/ |accessdate=2020-02-12 |agency=The Associated Press |publisher=CBS News |date=2015-06-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212183552/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/resignation-st-paul-minnesota-archbishop-john-nienstedt-sex-abuse-church/ |archivedate=2020-02-12 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

'''聖保祿教區'''於1850年7月設立，1888年5月4日升為總教區，1966年易名為「聖保祿及明尼波利斯總教區」。<ref name="History" />總教區於2015年1月申請[[破產保護|破產保護]]，2018年12月解除破產。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Wiering |first1=Maria |title=Archdiocese officially out of bankruptcy |url=https://thecatholicspirit.com/news/local-news/archdiocese-officially-out-of-bankruptcy/ |accessdate=2020-02-12 |publisher=The Catholic Spirit |date=2018-12-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212194426/https://thecatholicspirit.com/news/local-news/archdiocese-officially-out-of-bankruptcy/ |archivedate=2020-02-12 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>

